GETFINGERS

NAME
        GetFingers()



SYNOPSIS
        LIB_BODY: int GetFingers(string limb) LIB_ARMOR: int GetFingers()



DESCRIPTION
        For creatures, returns the number of fingers on the given limb. For armor, returns the number of fingers required to wear the item.



EXAMPLES
         



LOCATION
        /lib/body
/lib/std/armor
/lib/std/worn_storage


SEE ALSO
        AddFingers



Author
        Cratylus


